org.eclipse.modisco.workflow.modiscoworkflow
Interface WorkParameter

public interface WorkParameter

A representation of the model object ' Work Parameter'.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Direction
  • Type
  • Required
  • Description
  • Value
